HEADWORD: discombobulate
<hw>discombobulate</hw> <pos>v.</pos> <def>to cause to be confused;
confuse emotionally.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> confuse, flurry, consternate, disconcert, put off,
bewilder, bemuse, throw.</syn>⟦br⟧
